    <title>Setting Default Values on Select Menus.</title>
    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This tutorial will cover how to set the default value for a select menu (that isn&apos;t a text select menu)!</para>
<para><simplesect kind="note"><para><bold>This only works for the following types of select menus: user, role, mentionable, and channel.</bold> The default type of a select menu (as shown in <ref refid="components3" kindref="compound">this page</ref>) does not work for this, as that supports a &quot;placeholder&quot;.</para>
</simplesect>
